<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 18:09:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>印度工人在以色列排队上班，引发安全担忧和道德问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/safety-concerns-and-moral-questions-arise-as-indian-workers-queue-up-to-work-in-israel/0000018d-b1fe-dc8c-a3df-f3ff42220000</link><description>数量空前的印度人希望用自己祖国的失业来换取以色列相对较高的工资——以色列希望他们能取代数万名巴勒斯坦工人。据一些候选人称，众所周知，穆斯林不会被考虑</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 17:01:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/safety-concerns-and-moral-questions-arise-as-indian-workers-queue-up-to-work-in-israel/0000018d-b1fe-dc8c-a3df-f3ff42220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队播放在加沙发现的视频，显示 Bibas 一家于 10 月 7 日被扣为人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article-opinion/idf-airs-footage-found-in-gaza-showing-bibas-family-taken-hostage-in-first-days-of-war/0000018d-c1fc-dfbc-a3af-dbfd29e40000</link><description>Shiri 和 Yarden Bibas 以及他们 4 岁的孩子 Ariel 和当时 9 个月大的 Kfir 在基布兹 Nir ​​Oz 被绑架。这段视频显示了希里和红发儿童在汗尤尼斯被绑架的情景，这是继哈马斯去年 12 月发布亚登的视频后首次出现</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 16:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article-opinion/idf-airs-footage-found-in-gaza-showing-bibas-family-taken-hostage-in-first-days-of-war/0000018d-c1fc-dfbc-a3af-dbfd29e40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列灾难旅游需求量很大，但加沙边境社区的居民说“不要来”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-is-our-home-and-this-time-were-not-extending-invitations/0000018d-c143-df10-a99f-d7f33e030000</link><description>通常每年的这个时候，以色列人都喜欢前往西内盖夫观赏海葵花。但今年，正如一位当地人所说，“这就像在重症监护室的邻居家里举办派对一样”</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 15:53:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-is-our-home-and-this-time-were-not-extending-invitations/0000018d-c143-df10-a99f-d7f33e030000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争打击以色列经济 2023 年第四季度急剧下降 19.4%</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/gaza-war-hits-israeli-economy-with-19-4-drop-in-q4-of-2023/0000018d-c199-dfd7-a9fd-f39d2e500000</link><description>由于大量调动储备金和数万人流离失所，以色列 5000 亿美元的经济去年增长了 2.0%，而 2022 年将增长 6.5%</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 14:31:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/gaza-war-hits-israeli-economy-with-19-4-drop-in-q4-of-2023/0000018d-c199-dfd7-a9fd-f39d2e500000</guid></item><item><title>加沙评论后，外交部长将巴西总统标记为以色列不受欢迎的人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-minister-marks-brazilian-president-as-persona-non-grata-in-israel/0000018d-c136-df10-a99f-d7f751e70000</link><description>巴西总统卢拉将以色列在加沙的战争比作“希特勒决定屠杀犹太人”，这引发了巴西驻大屠杀纪念馆大使的谴责以及总统的严厉谴责</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 13:16:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-minister-marks-brazilian-president-as-persona-non-grata-in-israel/0000018d-c136-df10-a99f-d7f751e70000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列男子因轮奸 16 岁女孩被判处 22 至 14 年监禁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-men-given-22-14-years-in-prison-over-gang-rape-of-16-year-old-girl/0000018d-c13c-dfd7-a9fd-f3bc96bf0000</link><description>两名三十多岁的犯罪嫌疑人将在法庭判决后对受害人进行赔偿。涉案的另外八名男子将在晚些时候被判刑</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 13:14:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-men-given-22-14-years-in-prison-over-gang-rape-of-16-year-old-girl/0000018d-c13c-dfd7-a9fd-f3bc96bf0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院辩论以色列占领的合法性；内塔尼亚胡：听证会损害自卫权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/top-un-court-begins-hearings-into-israels-occupation-of-palestinian-territories/0000018d-c0c4-df10-a99f-d7f7f67e0000</link><description>国际法院开始就以色列占领约旦河西岸、加沙和东耶路撒冷问题举行为期六天的听证会，前所未有的 51 个国家将在听证会上发言</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/top-un-court-begins-hearings-into-israels-occupation-of-palestinian-territories/0000018d-c0c4-df10-a99f-d7f7f67e0000</guid></item><item><title>两项可能推翻内塔尼亚胡政府的法律草案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/two-draft-laws-that-could-bring-down-netanyahus-government/0000018d-c019-dfd7-a9fd-f39d96c60000</link><description>两项极不受欢迎的军事征兵法涉及以色列境内深刻的政治、安全和社会紧张局势，很可能成为内塔尼亚胡政府垮台的基石 — — 并将影响加沙战争的继续</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:26:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/two-draft-laws-that-could-bring-down-netanyahus-government/0000018d-c019-dfd7-a9fd-f39d96c60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列伞兵在加沙地带南部的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/israeli-paratrooper-killed-in-combat-in-southern-gaza-strip/0000018d-c095-df10-a99f-d7f7afcb0000</link><description>参谋军士。西蒙·什洛莫夫（Simon Shlomov）于2021年从哈萨克斯坦移民到以色列，当时是以色列陆军伞兵旅的一名孤独士兵</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:08:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/israeli-paratrooper-killed-in-combat-in-southern-gaza-strip/0000018d-c095-df10-a99f-d7f7afcb0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔的助手向同事、媒体人员和议员的妻子发放持枪许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-aides-hand-out-gun-permits-to-associates-media-personnel-and-lawmakers-wife/0000018d-c05f-dfd7-a9fd-f3dfea4b0000</link><description>在其平台上赞扬极右翼部长本-格维尔的媒体人士提交的许可证申请疑似在快速审批过程中获得批准，其中一些申请不符合标准</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-aides-hand-out-gun-permits-to-associates-media-personnel-and-lawmakers-wife/0000018d-c05f-dfd7-a9fd-f3dfea4b0000</guid></item><item><title>虽然以色列避免讨论加沙战争“第二天”，但巴勒斯坦人正在制定一项计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/while-israel-avoids-discussing-the-day-after-the-palestinians-are-working-on-a-plan/0000018d-c05d-dc8c-a3df-f27de4800000</link><description>由于担心其政治前途，哈马斯可能被迫加入巴解组织并承认其在加沙地带的地位。华盛顿、相关阿拉伯国家和巴勒斯坦组织目前正竞相为加沙的未来制定切合实际的工作计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 09:45:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/while-israel-avoids-discussing-the-day-after-the-palestinians-are-working-on-a-plan/0000018d-c05d-dc8c-a3df-f27de4800000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在美国压力下抵制国际社会承认巴勒斯坦国的呼吁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-fighting-intl-call-to-recognize-palestinian-state-under-u-s-pressure/0000018d-bdee-dc8c-a3df-ffff03880000</link><description>以色列总理内塔尼亚胡发起了反对单方面承认巴勒斯坦国的运动，称各方之间的直接谈判是建立巴勒斯坦国的唯一途径。虽然这是以色列全面采取的一项受欢迎的举措，但它可能无助于阻止国际认可</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 03:50:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-fighting-intl-call-to-recognize-palestinian-state-under-u-s-pressure/0000018d-bdee-dc8c-a3df-ffff03880000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会以微弱优势投票反对驱逐左翼议员，因为他支持国际法院针对以色列的种族灭绝案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/knesset-to-vote-on-expulsion-of-mk-ofer-cassif-over-signing-icj-petition/0000018d-bdec-dc8c-a3df-fffdab8b0000</link><description>此次驱逐投票是由于哈达什党议员在国际法院支持南非种族灭绝案件而引发的。此举需要议会120名议员中90名议员的批准，并得到85名议员的支持</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 03:39:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/knesset-to-vote-on-expulsion-of-mk-ofer-cassif-over-signing-icj-petition/0000018d-bdec-dc8c-a3df-fffdab8b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：担心被绑架的比巴斯家人的安全；以色列袭击黎巴嫩武器库</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article-live/pm-sides-with-far-right-to-limit-arab-israeli-visits-to-al-aqsa-during-ramadan/0000018d-bee3-dc8c-a3df-fef730a70000</link><description>以色列军队公布在加沙被绑架的比巴斯一家的视频 ■ 财政部长呼吁内塔尼亚胡如果对巴勒斯坦国采取任何单方面措施，就退出《奥斯陆协议》 ■ 也门胡塞武装称他们在红海击落船只并击落美国无人机</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 01:19:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article-live/pm-sides-with-far-right-to-limit-arab-israeli-visits-to-al-aqsa-during-ramadan/0000018d-bee3-dc8c-a3df-fef730a70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列关于斋月祈祷的决定是一场闹剧。可能会以悲剧告终</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-decision-on-ramadan-prayers-is-a-farce-it-could-end-in-tragedy/0000018d-be17-df10-a99f-bff71f5b0000</link><description>本·格维尔试图对阿克萨清真寺的阿拉伯裔以色列信徒实行全面限制，但并未完全成功。但这并没有阻止他幸灾乐祸——并冒着引发宗教冲突的风险</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 22:04:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-decision-on-ramadan-prayers-is-a-farce-it-could-end-in-tragedy/0000018d-be17-df10-a99f-bff71f5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院驳回加沙被拘留者寻求法律代表的请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-denies-petition-for-gaza-detainees-to-access-legal-representation/0000018d-be00-dd5e-a59d-ffb294300000</link><description>战争期间被拘留并被关押在以色列的 62 名加沙居民的家人要求提供有关他们及其拘留地点的信息。大法官以技术理由驳回请愿书，理由是请愿书涉及不同的案件，妨碍了清晰度</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 21:48:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-denies-petition-for-gaza-detainees-to-access-legal-representation/0000018d-be00-dd5e-a59d-ffb294300000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡支持极右翼要求，要求在斋月期间限制阿克萨清真寺的阿拉伯以色列信徒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-backs-far-right-demand-to-limit-arab-israeli-worshipers-at-al-aqsa-in-ramadan/0000018d-bd60-dc8c-a3df-ff75cc820000</link><description>信徒的年龄限制和居住区域将在即将进行的审议中确定，可能会根据警方的立场而定。安全官员警告总理不要阻止巴勒斯坦穆斯林进入阿克萨清真寺</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 20:27:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-backs-far-right-demand-to-limit-arab-israeli-worshipers-at-al-aqsa-in-ramadan/0000018d-bd60-dc8c-a3df-ff75cc820000</guid></item><item><title>拉马拉呼吁美国支持巴勒斯坦权力机构成为联合国会员国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/ramallah-calls-on-u-s-to-back-palestinian-authority-as-un-member-state/0000018d-bda8-dc8c-a3df-ffbd776d0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦权力机构的一名高级官员告诉《国土报》，国际社会在宣布两国解决方案的同时，还应该采取行动来证明其严肃性。巴勒斯坦权力机构总理表示，只要哈马斯接受“先决条件”，它准备与哈马斯合作</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 19:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/ramallah-calls-on-u-s-to-back-palestinian-authority-as-un-member-state/0000018d-bda8-dc8c-a3df-ffbd776d0000</guid></item><item><title>讲述以色列从第二次起义到有史以来最严重的加沙战争的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/telling-israels-story-from-the-second-intifada-to-its-worst-ever-gaza-war/0000018d-bc61-dd5e-a59d-fdf3f1d80000</link><description>以色列年度当地见证展览的最佳照片已汇集在一本书中。展览创始人 Dana Wohlfeiler-Lalkin 带我们经历个人和国家之旅</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 18:50:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/telling-israels-story-from-the-second-intifada-to-its-worst-ever-gaza-war/0000018d-bc61-dd5e-a59d-fdf3f1d80000</guid></item><item><title>历史性胜利：以色列游泳运动员在多哈世锦赛上获得银牌，遭到嘘声</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-swimmer-takes-silver-medal-booed-at-doha-world-championships/0000018d-bd78-dd5e-a59d-fdfa980b0000</link><description>“我很高兴来到这里，”阿纳斯塔西娅·戈尔本科说道，尽管卡塔尔首都的当地观众发出了嘘声。周日，她成为第一位在同一届世锦赛上两次闯入个人决赛的以色列人，在预赛中获得第五名</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 18:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-swimmer-takes-silver-medal-booed-at-doha-world-championships/0000018d-bd78-dd5e-a59d-fdfa980b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>